		"description": "<p dir=\"ltr\">You have put in the work and study to acquire specialized knowledge. You gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You learn a language of your choice and can speak, read, and sign it.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You can read a page of text in any language you know as an action.</p>\n</li>\n<li dir=\"ltr\" aria-level=\"1\">\n<p dir=\"ltr\" role=\"presentation\">You gain a single Scholarly Discovery from the scholar class. You must meet any prerequisites the discovery has to select it.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>",
